  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to alsa-oss</title>

    <para>
      The <application>alsa-oss</application> package contains
      the alsa-oss compatibility library. This is used by programs
      which wish to use the alsa-oss sound interface.
    </para>

    &lfs91_checked;

